/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the letter\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How would she feel about that?\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Would she send back her own AI-composed message, thanking the child for taking the time to write to her?\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own AI-composed message\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"the child\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read: The AI industry is stuck on one very specific way to use a chatbot The whole thing is bleak.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Read\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"The AI industry\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"one very specific way\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"a chatbot\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"The whole thing\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It takes the feel-good clich\\u00e9 of a child getting to interact with their idol and squishes a multimillion-dollar large language model between them.\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the feel-good clich\\u00e9\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"their idol\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"a multimillion-dollar large language model\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Google is pitching a world in which even the most personal interactions are mediated by computers.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9999956205270284, \"rank\": 4.37